WEBVTT

00:00:01.658 --> 00:00:07.604
Imagine a place where your neighbors
greet your children by name;

00:00:07.628 --> 00:00:10.931
a place with splendid vistas;

00:00:10.955 --> 00:00:14.066
a place where you can drive
just 20 minutes

00:00:14.090 --> 00:00:16.152
and put your sailboat on the water.

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.259
It's a seductive place, isn't it?

00:00:20.261 --> 00:00:21.857
I don't live there.

00:00:21.881 --> 00:00:24.430
(Laughter)

00:00:24.454 --> 00:00:30.473
But I did journey on a 27,000-mile trip